title: Dyllan Lanser
text:
Dyllan Lanser (born 2 March 1995) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="ASV%20De%20Dijk">ASV De Dijk</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> for <a href="Almere%20City%20FC">Almere City FC</a> on 14 September 2012 in a game against <a href="SC%20Cambuur">SC Cambuur</a>.
